{"tid":1892563,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警察飯局再一人出現病徵 (22:56)","createTime":"2020-02-22T15:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T16:04:05.000Z","uid":5195,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"338f373963dc909fd86f73e23b9d6ee73b0f94af","tid":1892563,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"一名駐守北角警署的48歲男警員早前接受測試，對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應。警方回覆查詢表示，截至今日（22日）晚上7時，有28名警務人員接獲通知，陸續入住檢疫中心接受檢疫。除確診者外，當晚共有59名警務人員出席飯局，至今5人出現病徵（較早前增加一名），其中兩人經接受醫院治療後已出院並入住檢疫中心，他們的初步檢疫結果呈陰性。其餘3名出現病徵的警務人員仍在醫院接受治療，當中兩人的初步檢疫結果呈陰性，一人正等候檢測結果。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，高度關注事件，積極配合衛生署的病理學追蹤，包括提交該名警員過去14日的工作紀錄和執勤表等資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200222/s00001/1582382871541/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%80%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%97%85%E5%BE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200222%2Fs00001%2F1582382871541%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2586%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BE%25B5&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2Bdgq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=13415b23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200222%2Fs00001%2F1582382871541%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2586%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BE%25B5&h=b2b07759\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200222/s00001/1582382871541/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9